Tigerhawk/Cheetor/Rhinox/Starwind/Depth Charge




Tigerhawk noticed no one had followed him. He could not let the 
maximals die. He was one of the few who knew what was at stake here. 
He flew above megatron and he four mini rockets at him [the mini 
rockets are half the size of the regular rockets so it's just like 
firing two missles.]



~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Cheetor switched out of battle mode. he put his blades together and 
fired a green blast at Megatron.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


Rhinox fired 25 rounds at Megatron.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


Starwind open his three front lazer gun points and fired at megatron.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Depth Charge flew next to Prowl. "well looks like the cf is gone."
